description:
Testimonies of Changed Lives - https://www.amazingfacts.org/news-and-features/changed-lives
 Share Your Testimony - https://www.amazingfacts.org/about-us/tell-your-story

By the time Vincent was 19, he had been swept away with the world. He listened to satanic music that blasphemed Jesus. In fact, his fall into darkness was so deep that, one day, while listening to this music, he carved 666 into the knuckles on his handdeep enough to make sure the scars stay. But when Amazing Facts Study Guides and DVDs made it into his hands, his life and his wife's began to change  and a wonderful, modern-day miracle of healing took place!
